ou need to play as the right "Civ" that is got traits that gain them extra culture. A good "civ" to play as is "Napoleon" because he gains culture from "chateau's". The game has a lot of DLC's, but luckily for you if you are considering getting Civilization 5 they have stopped making DLC's and are making Cilization 6 (this may sound like Civ 6 is coming out soon but no one knows) so steam have made it so for 34.99 you get Civilization 5 and all 11 DLC's including "BNW" (Brave New World) and GAK (Gods And Kings). this is a very good deal considering individualy it cost 78.35, so it is better than half priceand the DLC's make the game SOOOO much better its worth every penny. For a game where there is so much you can do either in muliplayer or in singleplayer giving you many hours of fun it is worth getting, i HIGHLY reccomend this game.
