ther ranged units to weaken the city. Price: Best thing about Civ 5 is that the price. You get a great game that gives you hours if not years of gameplay. Even tho it has been out since 2010 its well worth the asking price, on steam you can pick this game up for $30 or get the complete edition for $40. The complete edition comes with more civs and two expansion packs that add a lot of new gameplay features and just builds on an amazing game!
