-{PD}-SaxtonHaven.Lofticries;-;The game has good dialogue for civilization leaders. The game is very simple and fast paced. The tutorial and tips are very helpful. One of the best RTS with many mods which makes replay a new exciting experience each time. Rating: 10/10
