ohol, but those things will get you laid more thats for sure. Even moderation in moderation, go on blow a month or so on a Civ binge and learn how to manage your life, via the loss of every minute of time you can spare to the monkey overlord on your back. Do yourself a favor, get your video game addiction over with. Thats what this is gonna do for you, nothing will ever be the same.
