Eladria;-;For long time fans of the series, this makes some pretty dramatic changes, the ramifications of which may not be obvious at first glance. The removal of unit stacking leads to strategic city placement, and the dramatic increase in the use of Artillery units. For once, even on the easier difficulty levels, bombers and artillery play a part, instead of just stacking 15 tanks in one tile. Purchasing tiles and units feels almost like cheating, in the best of ways. If you enjoy 4X Games, give this an honest shot. It may take a bit of time, but soon, you'll wonder how you ever enjoyed playing the old way.
